                information stored in our data backups and archives, as required
                by law. Data on past transactions and data stored in backups and
                archives will be deleted in the normal course of EverWash's
                business. You may elect to opt-out at any time after registering
                for the EverWash service.
              </p>
              <h4>7. Access and Updating of Information</h4>
              <p>
                EverWash encourages you to view your transaction history, and
                review and amend your email address or contact details, in the
                EverWash platform at any time. Please contact us by sending an
                email to:
                <a href="mailto:support@everwash.com">support@everwash.com</a>
                or by using your settings window in the EverWash app.
              </p>
